sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant U as User
    participant FE as Frontend
    participant API as API Service
    participant OCR as OCR Module
    participant AI as AI Module
    participant IDX as Vector Index
    participant DB as SQL Store

    U->>FE: Upload document
    FE->>API: POST file + metadata
    API->>OCR: Parse image/text blocks
    OCR-->>API: text + confidence map
    API->>AI: classify and summarize
    AI->>IDX: write embeddings
    AI-->>API: tags + summary + entities
    API->>DB: save canonical record
    API-->>FE: return ready result
    FE-->>U: show insights dashboard